Items.Author: Viii
Items.Title: Single 'threadfear / ask me to stay' released
Items.Excerpt: New single 'threadfear' released with accompanying B-side, 'ask me to stay'.
Items.Content:
Viii's single 'threadfear' has just been released with the accompanying B-side cover of Etta Bond and Raf Riley's 'Ask Me To Stay'.

Check it out here. Out now on all digital music platforms.
